channel.title: I made a terrible mistake
channel.description: I modded Tru3scape last night on my server, editing several things. Number one I sped up the server (or so i though) by editing packets off a tutorial. Secondly I added a spell to my server using a command and also made pickup superadmin only and up. Well, it turns out now I cant use any commands at all. I removed everything that had to do with RS2 private servers, ran a full cookie+cash deletion and it still doesn't work. Even people that join my server can't do it. Please help.
